16 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
17 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 62 O.S. 2021, Section 195, is
18 amended to read as follows:
19 Section 195. A. 1. There is hereby created a petty cash fund
20 at each of the following institutions: Oklahoma School for the
21 Blind, Muskogee, Oklahoma; Oklahoma School for the Deaf, Sulphur,
22 Oklahoma; Griffin Memorial Hospital, Norman, Oklahoma; Eastern State
23 Hospital, Vinita, Oklahoma; Northern Oklahoma Resource Center of
24 Enid, Enid, Oklahoma; Southern Oklahoma Resource Center of Pauls
